title: DAVE HAUSE IN THE HURLEY STUDIOS
description: Earlier this year, singer of The Loved Ones and singer/songwriter Dave Hause spent a week at the Hurley Studios doing pre-production for his forthcoming record titled Devour. Press play to view all of the action and to hear Dave speak about making a new record and getting back on the road. See more from Dave
